: This module is a variant of the module  "Constructions" of Paul Byache.<br>
The aim is to build simple geometric pattern
<b>using rule and compass</b> with  the applet GeoGebra 3.
<br> As opposed to the original version of  P.Byache, the module
is destinated to students more advance in mathematics  (H3-H4). Hence a greater level
of exigence in the answers.
<br> For more interactivity,  when the answer is insufficient, the student construction
is sent back to be corrected.
<br>At the end of a correct correction, the student is asked to write
a  justification. The text is recorded for further  reading by the teacher.


